        <h2>Common Mistakes Jo Log Karte Hain</h2>
        <p>Baalon ko kala karne of jaldi mein log aksar kuch galtiyan karte hain jo situation and bigaad deti hain. In from bachein:</p>

        <p><strong>1. Chemical dyes pe depend hona:</strong> Ammonia-based hair dyes temporary dark colour dete hain lekin long-term mein follicles damage karte hain, scalp irritation hoti hai, and hair and tez white hone lagte hain. Natural methods slow hain lekin safe hain.</p>

        <p><strong>2. Ek remedy try karke chhod dena:</strong> Natural remedies mein patience chahiye — minimum 2-3 months consistently use do tabhi results aayenge. Ek hafta try karke "kaam nahi ofya" bolna fair nahi hai.</p>

        <p><strong>3. Sirf bahar from treatment karna:</strong> Bahar from mask and oil lagana important hai, lekin agar diet mein copper, B12, and iron nahi hai toh melanin production kaifrom hogi? Inside-out approach zaroori hai.</p>

        <p><strong>4. Stress ignore karna:</strong> Chronic stress cortisol badhata hai jo melanocyte stem cells ko damage karta hai. Harvard of research prove karti hai of stress directly greying cause karta hai. Stress management natural hair blackening ka integral part hai.</p>

        <p><strong>5. Hot water from hair dhona:</strong> Garam paani cuticles khol deta hai and pigment leach karta hai. Hamesha lukewarm ya cold water from hair dhoyein — especially tea/ckifee rinfrom ya henna ke baad.</p>

        <p><strong>6. Underlying deficiency ignore karna:</strong> Agar B12 ya iron bahut low hai toh koi also mask ya oil tab tak kaam nahi karega jab tak deficiency fix nahi hoti. Pehle blood test, phir remedy — ye sahi order hai.</p>

        <p><strong>7. Overnight mein result expect karna:</strong> Melanin production ek slow biological process hai. Hair growth cycle 3-6 months ka hota hai. Naye black hair tabhi dikhenge jab naya growth aayega — existing white hair andar from black nahi honge (except temporary methods like tea rinfrom ya henna).</p>

